{"tid":694354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋傳! 電話推銷遇「女會員 」啪啪啪  嬌喘56秒錄音 客服男瞬間「硬」化","createTime":"2018-06-08T08:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T09:21:10.000Z","uid":133529,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6694933ce2fceca755fce82dc61b2072e8e9d751","tid":694354,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T08:58:23.000Z","msg":"網搜小組／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n母湯喔！許多情侶為增加情趣，會在親密時故意接起電話或撥打電話給他人，增加刺激感，大陸近日出現一段客服人員打電話詢問後續服務，但女客人卻正在啪啪的刺激錄音，56秒的錄音也在網路上瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n近日一段大陸提供旅遊服務的客服電話錄音流出，一名男電話客服員致電給女會員，自我介紹並報上員工編號後說「您是在我們這邊註冊的會員用戶，這是我們對會員回訪，想問您後續有沒有考慮旅遊計畫？」<br />\n<br />\n「&hellip;什麼？」該名女子先是沉默後才回答，而客服員也不斷詢問，打算推廣自己的產品；沒想到，女子突然發出一串嬌喘，對著身旁的人說「嗯嗯&hellip;啊啊，我現在打電話呢&hellip;喜歡嗎？」，而客服人員也繼續專業的詢問，隨後錄音直接中斷。<br />\n<br />\n網友看完紛紛留言，「原來西施版上的事情真的會發生啊」、「羞恥play讚」、「母湯安捏」、「老司機在哪，快開車啊」、「誘騙我去當客服是吧」、「還不快開車呢，這小子真不懂事」、「哈哈哈哈太扯XD」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3334/d3334705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3334%2Fd3334705.jpg&h=61e146a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180607/1185624.htm#ixzz5Hp2x7vTv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180607%2F1185624.htm%23ixzz5Hp2x7vTv&d=cNpKoABIMS4UEtDN%2B8iTh%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4fb19eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180607/1185624.htm#ixzz5Hp2x7vTv</a>"},{"pid":"430ffab1f27b8a3bb726c43f96b91b55dcc9de5b","tid":694354,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd650b9a195d34c4bcfa3297a6f1cc6345f9c02","tid":694354,"uid":129335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:06:50.000Z","msg":"你老尾   巴士上聽到扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818672ed85b7eb6749e198bb8c3917374b43057d","tid":694354,"uid":21041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"又叫得幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2126d0551777c174b1dc6615a5a73c301482fbbd","tid":694354,"uid":133529,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"瘋傳都有片架，死人連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ba678a4357714b98d96a4df10b9ba09c63cd6d","tid":694354,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"想像永遠係美好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6f7253d386417ceff2c02a23a7ff8bef0ff450","tid":694354,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T09:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醜"}]}